
<sellerabr>AMERICAN BARRICK</sellerabr> {<sellercode>ABX</sellercode>} SELLS OHIO ASSETS
    TORONTO, April 2 - <seller>American Barrick Resources Corp</seller> said it
<status>sold</status> two <acquired>coal supply agreements and substantially all assets at
its two coal mines</acquired> in <acqloc>Ohio</acqloc> to {<purchaser>Peabody Coal Co</purchaser>} of Henderson,
